        </title>
        <p>
            Name, gender, and race have already been explained, as far as they need explaining, in <a href="../game_mechanics/secn_1.dai">"Game Mechanics, Section 1: Logging In"</a> and <a href="../game_mechanics/secn_2.dai">"Game Mechanics, Section 2: Creating A New Character"</a>.
