    <section id="profession">
        <title>
            Profession, alignment, &amp; faith
        </title>
        <p>
            Profession, alignment, and faith are currently very rudimentary. Every character is a mercenary, true neutral, and almost certainly a follower of the Tabernacle (it is possible not to be but there are currently no other deities to follow). As such these elements have no effect on gameplay.
        </p>
        <p>
            <strong>NOTE</strong>: You will often see players in-game and on the forums referring to mages, warriors, and priests. This is to do with which skills have been developed, chosen equipment, and preferred method of combat.
        </p>
    </section>
